Package: tariffTheme
Title: Custom Theme for Tariff Data Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Andreas", "Mayer", email = "andreas.mayer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Provides a custom ggplot2 theme and utilities for creating 
    consistent visualizations of tariff data. Includes a dark navy theme
    with light blue and yellow accents, functions for adding logos and borders,
    consistent text styling, and an example dataset of country tariffs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    cowplot,
    magick,
    grid,
    extrafont,
    data.table
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
